{"tid":523141,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"主播兒子成家　《101次求婚》女星當性感婆婆","createTime":"2018-01-08T09:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T10:44:03.000Z","uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8221387e080d22628024117e7295f287a4fdd622","tid":523141,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-LrcnnzUAojo/Usp0HQSPSwI/AAAAAAAAAJU/BNYmWvhnvwE/s1600/101%E6%AC%A1%E6%B1%82%E5%A9%9A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-LrcnnzUAojo%2FUsp0HQSPSwI%2FAAAAAAAAAJU%2FBNYmWvhnvwE%2Fs1600%2F101%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%25A9%259A.jpg&h=ce05a923&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n56歲日本女星淺野溫子1991年主演的日劇《101次求婚》，當年轟動亞洲，她和武田鐵矢的「美女野獸配」，成為不少日劇迷心目中的日劇經典。外型保養得宜的她，最近已升格當婆婆，她的33歲獨生子、NHK電視台主播魚住優，今天傳已於去年9月與同年的圈外女友登記結婚，上月舉行婚禮宴客，她對兒子終於成家，也相當開心。<br />\n<br />\n淺野溫子1983年與廣告劇作家、作詞家魚住勉結婚，之後生下兒子魚住優，魚住優是慶應大學畢業的高材生，大學畢業後曾在報社工作，10年前才轉到NHK電視台工作，目前擔任新聞主播，他與任職化妝品公司的女友交往4年多，終於在去年9月完婚。<br />\n<br />\n剛剛升格當婆婆的淺野溫子，近年來仍持續參與日劇、舞台劇演出，身材保養得宜的她，去年8月還為《週刊現代》拍攝性感寫真，難得以性感泳裝入鏡，火辣身材和凍齡外型令人稱羨。（蘇威全／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180108/1274384/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180108%2F1274384%2F&d=AQXv8v5zrInziDiuWMdLC%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=dc77f83e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180108%2F1274384%2F&h=ab842646\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180108/1274384/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180108/640_1fd035a227051bad30cbad0acc7a70be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180108%2F640_1fd035a227051bad30cbad0acc7a70be.jpg&h=ec64fbe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淺野溫子的獨子魚住優（右）是NHK電視台主播。翻攝電視畫面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180108/640_f845ac498b05259ffbfbd1b74055c332.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180108%2F640_f845ac498b05259ffbfbd1b74055c332.jpg&h=1539958e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淺野溫子去年8月為《週刊現代》拍攝性感辣照。翻攝《週刊現代》"},{"pid":"46ce3a2c70131e93a0e0778d97f2b06a40ea9f17","tid":523141,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T10:22:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04593188b815673a021d77720ba521603809ef87","tid":523141,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46ce3a2c70131e93a0e0778d97f2b06a40ea9f17","tid":523141,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T10:22:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T10:44:03.000Z","msg":"我先上"}]}